Title: Non-Abelian, Self-Dual Chern-Simons Vortices Coupled to Gravity
Authors: M. E. X. Guimar\~aes and L. A. J. London
Comments: 21 pages, LATEX, no figures
Report-no: GCR-95/06/01
Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D52 (1995) 6057-6064
\\
  In this article we consider $SU(2)$ Chern-Simons/Higgs theory coupled to
gravity in three-dimensions. It is shown that for a cylindrically symmetric
vortex both the Einstein equations and the field equations can be reduced to a
set of first-order Bogomol'nyi equations provided that we choose a specific
eighth-order potential.
